@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_pswsia(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.21 - v0 + 0.83)) - wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.73)))
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.abs(tmp + 0.41) / wp.cos(tmp + 0.50)))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.53 - v1 + 0.58) + wp.abs(v2 + 0.81)))
    v0 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
